1. Create an Account for every user.
2. In creating this account, generate the public and private keys.
3. When a user wants to start a conversation, do a lookup in the 
Accounts Collection using a key (probably username) and get their 
public key.
4. When sending a message, put the insert the encrypted text onto the 
server.
5. When outputting the texts on the UI, do a decrypt operator for every
message. (using the public keys of both users)
